{"word":"H1181 - בַּעֲלֵי בָּמֹות - Baʻălêy Bâmôwth - bah-al-ay' baw-moth' - Lords of the high places","slug":"H1181","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בַּעֲלֵי בָּמֹות</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Baʻălêy Bâmôwth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bah-al-ay' baw-moth'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Lords of the high places"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&#x05DC;&#x05D9; &#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05EA; - ba&#x201B;a&#x0306;le&#x0302;y ba&#x0302;mo&#x0302;th</b> - <i>bah-al-ay' baw-moth</i><p/>From the plural of <a href=\"#/H1168\">H1168</a> and the plural of <a href=\"#/H1116\">H1116</a>; <i>Baals of</i> (the) <i>heights</i>; <i>Baale Bamoth</i>, a place East of the Jordan: - lords of the high places."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1078\">H1078</a>, <a href=\"#/H1112\">H1112</a>, <a href=\"#/H1166\">H1166</a>, <a href=\"#/H1167\">H1167</a>, <a href=\"#/H1168\">H1168</a>, <a href=\"#/H1170\">H1170</a>, <a href=\"#/H1171\">H1171</a>, <a href=\"#/H1172\">H1172</a>, <a href=\"#/H1173\">H1173</a>, <a href=\"#/H1174\">H1174</a>, <a href=\"#/H1175\">H1175</a>, <a href=\"#/H1176\">H1176</a>, <a href=\"#/H1177\">H1177</a>, <a href=\"#/H1178\">H1178</a>, <a href=\"#/H1179\">H1179</a>, <a href=\"#/H1180\">H1180</a>, <a href=\"#/H1182\">H1182</a>, <a href=\"#/H1183\">H1183</a>, <a href=\"#/H1184\">H1184</a>, <a href=\"#/H1185\">H1185</a>, <a href=\"#/H1186\">H1186</a>, <a href=\"#/H1187\">H1187</a>, <a href=\"#/H1188\">H1188</a>, <a href=\"#/H1189\">H1189</a>, <a href=\"#/H1190\">H1190</a>, <a href=\"#/H1191\">H1191</a>, <a href=\"#/H1192\">H1192</a>, <a href=\"#/H1193\">H1193</a>, <a href=\"#/H1195\">H1195</a>, <a href=\"#/H1196\">H1196</a>"}]}